      "utterance": "完成！所有字段已配置完毕。让我确认一下：Version和Identification都映射到Education_ContentCDN，IHL和Destination Address映射到Education_LMS_Portal，StudentDB承担了Type of Service、Fragment Offset、Protocol、Header Checksum、Source Address和Options六个字段，ClassroomService负责Total Length和Time to Live，GradeSync对应Flags，Padding保持原样。",
